---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Web Design Client Terms - Chiltern Computers"
  description="Terms and conditions for web design services provided by Chiltern Computers. Intellectual property, hosting, licensing, and support terms."
  noindex={true}
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
    { name: 'Web Design', url: '/services/web-design/' },
    { name: 'Client Terms', url: '/web-design-terms/' },
  ]}
>
  <div class="section-bg-1" style="padding: 120px 20px 80px; min-height: 100vh;">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
        <h1
          class="space-font galaxy-text cosmic-glow"
          style="font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 48px); margin-bottom: 16px;"
        >
          Web Design Client Terms
        </h1>
        <div
          style="height: 3px; width: 120px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--plasma-cyan), var(--aurora-green)); margin: 0 auto 20px; border-radius: 2px;"
        >
        </div>
        <p
          class="alien-font"
          style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 16px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;"
        >
          Last updated: March 2026
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Terms Content -->
      <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 40px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            1. Intellectual Property &amp; Ownership
          </h2>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            All website source code, design files, templates, components, animations, and
            underlying architecture created by Chiltern Computers remain the intellectual property
            of Chiltern Computers (David Hagon) at all times. This includes but is not limited to:
          </p>
          <ul
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 24px;"
          >
            <li>HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and framework source code</li>
            <li>Design layouts, colour schemes, and visual compositions created for the project</li>
            <li>Custom animations, interactions, and component logic</li>
            <li>Build configurations, deployment scripts, and hosting setup</li>
            <li>SEO configuration, structured data markup, and performance optimisations</li>
          </ul>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >
            The client is granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable licence to use the completed
            website for their business purposes for the duration of the service agreement. This
            licence does not include the right to copy, redistribute, resell, or repurpose the
            source code or design for any other website or project.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            2. What the Client Owns
          </h2>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            The client retains full ownership of:
          </p>
          <ul
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 24px;"
          >
            <li>Their business name, branding, and logo</li>
            <li>Written content and copy they provide or commission</li>
            <li>Photographs and images they supply</li>
            <li>Their domain name (registered in the client's name)</li>
            <li>Any data collected through their website (contact form submissions, etc.)</li>
          </ul>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >
            The client's domain name is always registered in their own name and remains their
            property regardless of the status of the service agreement.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            3. Source Code &amp; Handover
          </h2>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            Source code (the original development files used to build the website) is not included
            in any web design package and will not be provided to the client. The client receives
            a live, deployed, fully functional website — not the underlying code repository.
          </p>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >
            The built output (compiled HTML, CSS, and JavaScript served to visitors) is publicly
            accessible as part of any live website. This compiled output is minified and optimised
            for performance, and does not constitute the source code or development files.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            4. Hosting &amp; Infrastructure
          </h2>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            Websites are hosted on infrastructure managed by Chiltern Computers. Hosting is
            included free for the first year from the date of deployment. After the first year,
            hosting is subject to a small annual renewal fee.
          </p>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >
            The hosting account and deployment pipeline remain under the control of Chiltern
            Computers. If the client wishes to move their domain to a different provider, they
            are free to do so at any time — however, the existing website code and hosting
            configuration will not be transferred.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            5. Modifications &amp; Updates
          </h2>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            Content updates (text changes, new images, adding a service, etc.) are handled by
            Chiltern Computers on behalf of the client. Minor updates are included as part of
            ongoing support. Larger changes or new features may be quoted separately.
          </p>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >
            The client must not attempt to modify, reverse-engineer, decompile, or create
            derivative works from the website code. Any unauthorised modification may void
            support and hosting arrangements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            6. Copying &amp; Duplication
          </h2>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            The client may not copy, duplicate, scrape, or extract the website design, code, or
            structure for use on another website — whether for themselves or a third party. This
            includes hiring another developer to replicate or recreate the site based on the
            design and functionality provided by Chiltern Computers.
          </p>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >
            Each website is a bespoke creation. Unauthorised duplication is a breach of these
            terms and may result in legal action to protect intellectual property rights.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            7. Termination &amp; Cancellation
          </h2>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            Either party may terminate the service agreement with 30 days' written notice. Upon
            termination:
          </p>
          <ul
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 24px;"
          >
            <li>The website will be taken offline at the end of the notice period</li>
            <li>The client retains ownership of their domain name and can point it elsewhere</li>
            <li>The client retains ownership of any content and images they provided</li>
            <li>Source code and hosting infrastructure are not transferable</li>
            <li>No refund is due for the initial build fee after the website has been delivered</li>
          </ul>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >
            If the client fails to pay the annual hosting renewal within 30 days of the due date,
            Chiltern Computers reserves the right to suspend or remove the website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            8. Portfolio &amp; Showcase Rights
          </h2>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >
            Chiltern Computers reserves the right to display the completed website in its
            portfolio, marketing materials, and case studies, unless the client requests
            otherwise in writing before the project begins.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            9. Liability
          </h2>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >
            Chiltern Computers will make reasonable efforts to keep the website online and
            functioning correctly. However, liability is limited to the fees paid for the service.
            Chiltern Computers is not liable for loss of business, revenue, or data arising from
            website downtime, third-party service outages, or issues beyond reasonable control.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            10. Governing Law
          </h2>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >
            These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of England and
            Wales. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of
            England and Wales.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Summary Box -->
        <div
          style="background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1); border: 2px solid var(--plasma-cyan); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-top: 32px;"
        >
          <h3
            class="space-font"
            style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center;"
          >
            IN PLAIN ENGLISH
          </h3>
          <ul
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 24px;"
          >
            <li>I build and host your website — you get a live site that works for your business</li>
            <li>You own your domain name, your content, and your images</li>
            <li>I own the code, design, and technical setup — it stays with me</li>
            <li>You cannot copy the site or give the code to someone else</li>
            <li>If you want to leave, you take your domain and content — the site stays with me</li>
            <li>Hosting is free for the first year, then a small annual fee to keep it online</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <div
          style="background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1); border: 1px solid var(--plasma-cyan); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-top: 24px;"
        >
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="color: var(--starlight-white); font-size: 14px; margin: 0;"
          >
            Questions about these terms? Get in touch:<br />
            david@chilterncomputers.net | 07971 331814
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--plasma-cyan);"
        >
          <a href="/services/web-design/" class="space-button">
            View Web Design Packages
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
